property.name: dialog
property.value: So you've found me. No doubt at this point you're beginning to wonder about the nature of the... "Twist..." Aren't you?

property.name: dialog
property.value: Hmm, well I guess you've followed me this far... I can give you a clue.

property.name: dialog
property.value: We are inside a game, and it is a special game. There's a quality it has, which makes it... Scarce.

property.name: dialog
property.value: Well, think about other things that have scarcity... Money, time, food...

property.name: dialog
property.value: I'm afraid that's all I can tell you for now...

property.name: option2
property.value: I mean if you could make a better forest...

property.name: dialog
property.value: ... If that's how you want to play, we can play.
